article.description: — Andre Curbelo scored 24 points as Southern Miss beat Texas State 78-74 on Saturday night.
article.headline: Curbelo puts up 24, Southern Miss takes down Texas State 78-74
article.linkText: Curbelo puts up 24, Southern Miss takes down Texas State 78-74
article.story: HATTIESBURG, Miss. -- — Andre Curbelo scored 24 points as Southern Miss beat Texas State 78-74 on Saturday night. Curbelo also added five rebounds for the Golden Eagles (15-12, 8-6 Sun Belt Conference). Austin Crowley scored 19 points and added five rebounds and five assists. Tegra Izay shot 4 of 5 from the field to finish with nine points, while adding six rebounds and three blocks. Jordan Mason led the way for the Bobcats (11-16, 4-10) with 18 points and two steals. Texas State also got 17 points and three steals from Coleton Benson. Chris Nix also put up 10 points and six rebounds. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
